frames.caption: A young boy joyfully rides on the back of a roaring dinosaur, surrounded by a lush prehistoric landscape. In the sky, a pterosaur soars gracefully, adding to the dynamic scene. The sunlight filters through the trees, casting a warm glow over the entire setting.
frames.description: The scene is set in a vibrant prehistoric jungle, filled with towering trees and dense foliage. A boy is seen riding a dinosaur, with other dinosaurs visible in the background. The atmosphere is adventurous and exhilarating, capturing a moment of pure excitement and wonder.

frames.caption: A majestic scene unfolds in a prehistoric jungle as a large dinosaur moves through the dense foliage. Above, a pterosaur soars gracefully against a backdrop of a golden sky. The interplay of light and shadow highlights the textures of the dinosaur's skin and the vibrant greenery around.
frames.description: The scene is set in a prehistoric jungle environment, featuring a large dinosaur in the foreground and a flying pterosaur in the sky. The atmosphere is serene yet awe-inspiring, capturing the grandeur of the ancient world.
